ng to Automation\\n\\tDCS, PLC, testing and commission.\\n\\t SINO-PEC Baling branch/ Power Plant LV switchgear updating.\\n\\t SINO-PEC Baling branch/ Epoxy- Resin Department switchgear updating.\\n\\t SINO-PEC Changling branch/ Catalyst Plant switchgear updating.\\n\\t SINO-PEC Changling branch / Changsheng PP plant electrical system maintenance\",\"title\":\"E&I Enginerring\",\"rangeDate\":\"2005-7至2009-9\"}]', '[\"Electrical Maintenance\",\"Instrumentation\",\"DCS\",\"PLC\"]', 'wang-yacong-8a82bb41', '2017-05-17 16:03:13');
INSERT INTO `linkedin_data` VALUES ('50621', 'Walee', 'Wang', '化学', 'Technical Services Manager, Additives, Asia at Troy Corporation', '中国', '[{\"active\":true,\"schoolName\":\"安徽理工大学\"},{\"active\":true,\"schoolName\":\"University of Canberra\"}]', '[{\"locationName\":\"中国 上海市区\",\"companyName\":\"Shanghai Vision Chemicals\",\"description\":\"-Lead team to develop high performance coatings like architecture coatings and general industrial coatings and universal colorants and so on. \\n\\n- Responsible for products improvement and support manufacturing process team to launch products successfully. Compile products TDS and leaflets and brochures to support sales team and distributors for better promotion in China market.\",\"title\":\"Senior Product Development (Coatings)\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(cn,8909)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2002-7至2005-5\"},{\"locationName\":\"中国 上海市区\",\"companyName\":\"Shanghai Rock Paint Co., LTd\",\"description\":\"-Set up R&D and technical service team, and focused on architecture coatings and general industrial coatings research and development.\\n\\n-Start to get in touch of different coatings formulations and raw materials like pigments, extenders, additives, emulsions, resins, dispersions, colorants, etc.\\n\\n-Lead team to development new different formulations to support sales team growth, and improve old formulations properties to reduce cost greatly. Besides, set up car refinish coatings system like base coat and colorants.\\n\\n-Prepare related TDS and leaflets to support sales team and marketing team and provide necessary technical services to customers.\",\"title\":\"Product Development Engineer\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(cn,8909)\",\"rangeDate\":\"1998-9至2001-7\"},{\"locationName\":\"中国 上海市区\",\"companyName\":\"Nippon Paint China\",\"description\":\"-Responsible for product development and improvement of architecture coatings and anti-corrosion coatings like protective & Marine coatings. \\n\\n-Provide necessary technical services to key account customers or distributors.\",\"title\":\"Technical Engineer (Coatings)\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(cn,8909)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2001-7至2002-7\"},{\"locationName\":\"中国 上海市区\",\"companyName\":\"Elementis Specialties\",\"description\":\"-Manage technical service team to focus on additives application and services in architecture coatings, protective &marine coatings, general industrial coatings, colorants, inks, adhesives and construction.\\n\\n-Lead team to support China and Asia business growth through technical activities like customer calls, technical projects, seminars and workshops, trouble-shooting. \\n\\n-Make open technical presentations on rheology modifiers, wetting and dispersants, green additives, technical total solution etc. in different application systems.\\n\\n-Support global new-products application development through team lab work research activities and give valuable suggestion and recommendations. \\n\\n-Consolidate and integrate various additives portfolio like organoclays, organic thixotropes thickeners such as castor oil base, polyamide, mix-diamide, polyolefin, liquid thixotrope, HASE and PUR thickeners, wetting and dispersants, defoamers, etc.\\n\\n- Closely work together commercial team such as sales and marketing, and participate sales tools such as application leaflets, brochures, newsletters etc.\",\"title\":\"Technical Service Manager\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(cn,8909)\",\"honors\":[\"urn:li:fs_honor:(ACoAAAR0qoABqr51vF9fQPLrfsbAc3l-TI30Nu0,31)\"],\"rangeDate\":\"2005-5至2013-12\"},{\"locationName\":\"中国 上海市区\",\"companyName\":\"Troy Corporation\",\"description\":\"-Be responsible for setting up China lab center and Asia additives application system to support Asia additives business organic growth.\\n\\n-Technical management for Asia additives labs including Bangkok lab and Shanghai lab including personnel management.\\n\\n-Managing and overseeing technical services activities like customer calls, presentations, in-house training, workshop and seminars.\\n\\n-Managing technical projects in performance additives in coating, inks and adhesive systems.\\n\\n-Participating in global additives business team in marketing and commercial strategies and decisions.\\n\\n-Making creative and innovative recommendation to global leaders and contributing technical solutions or suggestions to whole organization.\",\"title\":\"Technical Services Manager, Additives, Asia\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(cn,8909)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2014-1\"}]', '[\"Additives\",\"Colorants\",\"Ink\",\"Coatings\"]', 'walee-wang-99405021', '2017-05-17 16:03:16');
INSERT INTO `linkedin_data` VALUES ('50622', 'Wang', 'RUI', '食品和饮料', 'STARCH SPECIALIST - Tianjin tungfung starch develop co,ltd', '中国', '[]', '[{\"locationName\":\"Tianjin CHINA\",\"companyName\":\"Tianjin tungfung starch develop co,ltd\",\"description\":\"As a Product Technology Specialist, In charge for the technology of product, the evaluation of new production, training the sales with new product, service for the vip customers . Solve the problems about product and process in different factories Tianjin、Hangzhou and Thailand. Then Report to manager.\",\"title\":\"starch specialist\",\"rangeDate\":\"2012-7\"},{\"locationName\":\"TIANJIN CHINA\",\"companyName\":\"Tianjin tungfung starch develop co,ltd.\",\"description\":\"Application of R&D,As a Application engineer, in charge for the applications of different modified starch . Such as dairy, baking food, meat, and so on .I also keep maintain, continually build, and systematically share knowledge of modified starch products with customers. Regular communication, get competitive intelligence,and help to solve the problems in producing, to meet and innovation customer demand.\\n As a production engineer, in charge for the exploitation new modified starch. For example ,Acetylated starch,Acetylated distarch adipate,Acid treated starch,Hydroxypropyl starch and so on .Charge for the SAP of R&D .Master the property of these starchs ,and knew how to produce. Create new recipe, improve the process ,cut down the cost initiatives. Familiar with laws and regulations of China, and keep contact with the government and the modified starch association . Next I analysis some products of other competitive companys which from Europe and USA . and so on.\",\"title\":\"Application Engineer、Production Engineer、Supervisor\",\"rangeDate\":\"2004-7至2009-2\"},{\"locationName\":\"Hangzhou\",\"companyName\":\"Hangzhou starpro co,ltd\",\"description\":\"1. Create a new laboratory for MS in Hangzhou city for 3 years. Training some new staffs.\\n2. Work with sales and find the potential requirements of customers.\\n3. Develop new products, new materials and help production to produce in different factories.\\n4. Make specifications, solve anomaly, Training sales and customers for new products.\\n5. Keep contact with the government and the modified starch association . \\n6. Complete the task which from leader .Make the plan, budget of BU for next year.\\n7. Support to the OEM factories.\\n8. SAP / ERP of R&D\",\"title\":\"Manager of production in R&D\",\"rangeDate\":\"2009-2至2012-7\"}]', '[\"SAP\",\"Leadership\",\"R&D\",\"Food\"]', 'wang-rui-2b1aaa31', '2017-05-17 16:03:17');
INSERT INTO `linkedin_data` VALUES ('50623', 'Wang', 'Lei (Philip)', '金融服务', 'HR General Manager (Wanda Internet Finance Group, Shanghai), previously at Disney, Bosch and Intel', '上海 浦东新区', '[{\"active\":true,\"schoolName\":\"南开大学\"}]', '[{\"locationName\":\"China\",\"companyName\":\"Dalian Wanda Group\",\"description\":\"Responsible for Executive Recruitment for Wanda Financial Group, target to fulfill positions are Director and above levels. \",\"title\":\"Recruitment Director\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(cn,0)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2015-8至2016-7\"},{\"locationName\":\"中国 上海市区\",\"companyName\":\"Shanghai Disney Resort\",\"description\":\"- Recruitment Execution –- assist recruitment director to define and execute overall recruitment strategy to support various talents needs for Shanghai Disney Resort before park opening.\\n\\n- Recruitment Marketing –- define EVP for Shanghai Disney Resort, and based on this, develop proper communication and recruitment marketing plan to drive enough application.\\n\\n- Campus Relations Management –- define campus strategy, lead team to develop and maintain favorable relations with key target schools for short and long term talent supply.\",\"title\":\"HR Manager – Recruitment Marketing & Campus Relations\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(cn,8909)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2013-9至2015-8\"},{\"locationName\":\"Shanghai\",\"companyName\":\"万达集团\",\"description\":\"Responsible for general HR management for Wanda Internet Finance Group (incl. recruitment, C&B, T&D, HR service etc.)\",\"title\":\"General Manager HR (Wanda Internet Finance Group)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2016-8\"},{\"locationName\":\"中国 上海市区\",\"companyName\":\"Intel Asia-Pacific R&D Ltd.\",\"description\":\"- Manager Counseling & Employee Development – provide counseling to 20+ first-line managers on the topics of team development and people management etc.\\n\\n- Employee Relations and Engagement – conduct employee satisfaction survey, timely build up action plans to address the gap and enhance employee engagement level.\\n\\n- Transition & Change Management – help business group form the new org-structure during its org-change period, facilitate people movement and organize according employee trainings.\",\"title\":\"HR Business Partner\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(cn,8909)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2008-5至2009-10\"},{\"locationName\":\"中国 上海市区\",\"companyName\":\"Bosch (China) Investment Ltd.\",\"description\":\"Start with \'Bosch Junior Manager Program\' in first two years with cross-country (Germany Bosch Headquarter), cross-function (Marketing & Communication Dept.), and cross division (Power Tools Division) rotations. Upon sussessful completion, promoted to manage the Corporate Employer Branding Team with following responsible areas: \\n\\n- Employer Branding Communication and Promotion – lead all Bosch China’s 40+ subsidiaries and joint-ventures, based on EVP, set up overall strategy to communicate and promote Bosch Ideal-Employer image to target groups.\\n\\n- Talent Recruitment Platform and Event Management – manage and continuously optimize recruitment platform and channels to attract qualified candidates in the War of Talent; organize recruitment events both in China and overseas.\\n\\n- Social Media Management – carry out social media strategy on HR relevant topic; conduct general supervision of social media platform and topic.\",\"title\":\"HR Manager - Employer Branding & Recruitment\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(cn,8909)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2009-10至2013-9\"}]', '[\"Marketing Communications\",\"Project Management\",\"Employer Branding\",\"Social Media\"]', 'wang-lei-philip-4751357', '2017-05-17 16:03:17');
INSERT INTO `linkedin_data` VALUES ('50624', 'Huilong', 'Wang', '设计', 'Product Manager & Accessory Designer at OnePlus', '广东 深圳', '[{\"active\":true,\"schoolName\":\"浙江大学\"},{\"active\":true,\"schoolName\":\"新加坡国立大学\"},{\"active\":true,\"schoolName\":\"瑞典兰德大学\"}]', '[{\"locationName\":\"丹麦哥本哈根地区\",\"companyName\":\"Nicholai Wiig Hansen Design\",\"description\":\"My main responsibility is to visualise products by 3D modelling, rendering and present to our clients. Main projects includes furniture, jewellery and home accessories design.\",\"title\":\"Product Internship\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(dk,5038)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2012-10至2013-2\"},{\"locationName\":\"Stockholm, Sweden\",\"companyName\":\"Front design\",\"description\":\"Product design internship. Working range from ideation, hand sketching, 3D modelling and mockup making. The clients include Louis Vuitton, Haagen-Dazs, Ballantine, Mutto (Swedish furniture company), etc.\",\"title\":\"Design Assistant\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(se,8064)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2013-2至2013-7\"},{\"locationName\":\"Ämhult, Sweden\",\"companyName\":\"IKEA\",\"description\":\"I proposed a design strategy and helped IKEA to realise a 3-week research in Mainland China. I was responsible for data analyse, and offered several design solutions expressed by sketches, 3D models, prototypes and stories. The outcomes were published on IKEA’s intranet. My contribution were used as a part of their pre-research and provide idea inspirations for their future work.\",\"title\":\"Master Thesis\",\"rangeDate\":\"2012-1至2012-6\"},{\"locationName\":\"中国 广东 深圳\",\"companyName\":\"OnePlus\",\"description\":\"Accountable for OnePlus Lifestyle Products as the product manager, as well as the chief designer of Lifestyle products.\",\"title\":\"Product Manager & Product Designer\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(cn,8910)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2015-4\"},{\"locationName\":\"中国\",\"companyName\":\"emoi\",\"description\":\"I created several series of products including tableware and teapot set, which achieved a remarkable success on the market. I took the responsibility for these products from designing to producing. Apart from that, I was also in charge of product planning, product characters and competition analyse, and users feedback.\",\"title\":\"Product Designer\",\"rangeDate\":\"2013-8至2015-2\"}]', '[\"Design Strategy\",\"Design Research\",\"Process Design\",\"Hand Sketching\"]', 'huilong-wang-5695362b', '2017-05-17 16:03:18');
INSERT INTO `linkedin_data` VALUES ('50625', 'Joris', 'Wang', '零售', 'Logistic unit Capacity & flow planning /Expansion supplying project leader', '中国 上海市区', '[]', '[{\"locationName\":\"中国 上海市区\",\"companyName\":\"宜家\",\"description\":\"project leader:\\n• Responsible for the New store implementation process: secure all the key point of the checklist is working under timeline, all working partners, RST, IT, store logistic, sales, etc, are ongoing according to the time line. \\n• Leading the supplying project meeting: timely update the project on going situation to working partners; coordinate and solve any supplying issues happened during the whole project from the first kick off meeting till store opening. \\n• Accountable for the order plan process, coaching to the planner and borrowed resources regarding a higher quality order planning and follow up performance.\\ncapacity & flow planning:\\nLogistic capacity:\\n• Monitor and report the store capacity situation and planned development over a five-year period for inclusion in the overall supply chain capacity planning. The five-year plan will also be the input to store board meeting.\\nMonitoring the capacity situation of total CN market; input to Retail logistic manager the necessary logistic solution on general level; input to the Sales manager for the range direction. \\nReplenishment solution:\\n• Based on replenishment performance of upstream supply chain, work with regional supply team to define most optimal replenishment solution for different store cluster, aiming to have a balance between capacity and supply chain cost. \\n• peak day management: as a task leader to pre-plan the sales peak day such as CNY, Forecast the store capacity situation and work with purchasing, transport, warehouse to work out the scenario plan.\\nProject:\\n • Retail representative of Multi-Channel Distribution Network 2030 project member: working with AP distribution group, analyse store capacity, sales growth, transport develop and sourcing trend. Workout the logistic unit mapping with both logistic and cost efficiency. This project is support IKEA’s growth in different sales channels in 10-15 years’ time horizon. \\n• Project member of CN e-commerce; DC expansion and CDC expansion.\",\"title\":\"Logistic unit Capacity & flow planning /Expansion supplying project leader\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(cn,8909)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2014-1\"},{\"companyName\":\"DHL\",\"description\":\"Allocation planner.\\n-\\tAd-hoc Prediction plan. Responsible for the volume plan before peak time such as Spring Festival so as to ensure the sufficient allocation during this period.\\n-\\tRegular allocation plan. Responsible for allocation plan yearly or quarterly then to negotiate the agreement with the airline company in terms of price, pivot weight and the arrangement of the allotment.\\n-\\tLead and monitor the trends of the total allocation cost by CPK report. Analyze the main reason of the cost hit and input to the department strategic plan.\\nKPI responsible\\n-\\tResponsible for Dept KPI. Analyze the process efficiency. Support operation team to the I/E process efficiency improvement.\",\"title\":\"Gateway Transportation Associate\",\"rangeDate\":\"2004-12至2006-12\"},{\"companyName\":\"Sailatto Shanghai Office\",\"description\":\"-\\tArrange the transportation of the cargos. Prepare the related documents to the custom broker and the agent office so as to ensure the customer receives the cargo in time. \\n-\\tCoordinate with the freight forwarder, the I/E agent in terms of the import issues; \\n-\\tContact the foreign company regarding trade affairs.\",\"title\":\"Customer Service Executive\",\"rangeDate\":\"2004-2至2004-12\"},{\"companyName\":\"IKEA China (Investment) Co.,LTD\",\"description\":\"-\\tResponsible for the accuracy of production plan and replenishment plan from supplier. Analyze the deviation reason; solution provided to the related dept regarding FC error, order delayed, etc.\\n-\\tLead and