production line equipment design and production process design. Responsible development building materials business of foreign trade. Cooperation with clients and construction project bidding.\\n\\n\\n We are the vermiculite boards and Perlite board supplier in Shanghai of China,we also provide building materials assembly line production equipment, including according to the requirements of customers design, manufacture and installation guide equipment. \\n Boards are made from a mineral called vermiculite. We exfoliated these vermiculites and mix with proprietary chemicals bonding. It then undergoes a heating and pressing process and our boards are formed \\n We are aware of the importance of what difference can be made when there is fire protection being installed onto a building; it safeguards properties and most importantly the lives of people.\\n we specialize in the production of fire-proofing boards which fulfils this purpose and has a wide range of application in the building materials category while the product itself carries the following unique features: light weight, incombustible, sound proofing, toxic-free, environmentally healthy and insect- free. Our boards are made from vermiculite which underwent an exfoliating process at our factory and with our unique processing methods where the boards became end products in a panel form. \\n Applications of vermiculite board are endless; here are just a few examples:\\n Fire proofing doors \\n Partition panel \\n Wall claddings \\n Ceiling \\n Decorative furniture \\n Platforms for marine and vessels \\n industrial furnace\\nour company also produce the equipments of vermiculite board and Perlite board\",\"title\":\"The marketing director\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(cn,8909)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2011-11\"},{\"locationName\":\"Marketing\",\"companyName\":\"AAC\",\"description\":\"1. formulate the strategic plan. 2. market promotion of the product and service. 3. manage the sales department and assess the performance. 4. look for new profit point and develop new bussiness. 5. in charge of cooperation and deal with the government department.6. in charge of market survey of different cities.7. write the bussiness plan, help the general manage to negotiate with venture capitalist.8.promote the sale of database.9. establish and manage the operation system of the company, plan and direct of ERP and CRM system.10. Advertisement and cooperation with the media. 11. develop distributor for the clients and manage the distributors. In the period in this company, also cooperate with Gonow auto, help them start from zero to establish sale network and operation system, plan and train the CRM and ERP system\\nAchievements:\\t1. through cooperatative sale, improve the insurance and service bussiness 30% per month.3. held business cocktail, self-travel and Christmas party at low cost. 4. successfully promote the database bussiness to CARTEC、SIMOEIZE, JABRA bluetooth headset, ST Electronics, Valvoline Maxlife Motor Oil and Mobil Oil.5. Establish informative and detail database of market research, provide substantial base for the develoment of the company.\",\"title\":\"Marketing manager\",\"rangeDate\":\"2004-12至2007-4\"},{\"locationName\":\"Representative office\",\"companyName\":\"HK OYT Holdings Co., LTD\",\"description\":\"1.in charge of building up sale system in China, formulating the strategic plan and development direction. 2. in charge of market promotion in China (new product). 3. in charge of distributor development. 4. build up the management system, procedure and rules of the factory and sale. 2.formulate the management system of distributor. 6.plan and implement of market promotion. 7. formulate and implement the advertisement. 8. Development of cash flow control system \\nAchievements:\\tInitially in china. people are not familiar the product, I do a lot of information search to improve the product introduction, a lot of work has been done for market promotion to make the clients know and accept this enviornmental fire protection product, develp 4 value added partner with high \\nprestige,establish long term cooperative relationship with 15 big clents in china.At the first half year improve the sales amount from 100,000 to more than 3000,000 in the second year in china, sign the long term cooperative contract with four big companies, the sale amount is 6,000,000, it became 11,000,000, 20,000,000 and 26,000,000 in 2009, 2010 and 2011 respectively in china, Plus I develop foreign large quantities of long-term orders, the production capacity of the factory saturate and prepare to buy new production line to enlarge the production. According to the factory siutation, establish the management system, procedure and rules, make the company enter the normal operation of the track. Also in charge of product development and design of the installation drawing.\",\"title\":\"Chief representative\",\"rangeDate\":\"2007-4至2011-11\"}]', '[\"Market Research\",\"Product Development\",\"Negotiation\",\"Management\"]', 'wang-lei-a1914838', '2017-05-17 16:04:10');
