the inventory reonciliaiton projects with all distributors and successfully built strong business partnerships\\n*Built and developed the global revenue accounting team, quoted \\\"the best revenue team ever\\\" by the audit partner\\n*Implemented Oracle Channel/ Trade Management on time, on budget as the business lead; a business case was written and published by Oracle for the successful implementation\",\"title\":\"Coporate Revenue Controller (Jul 2010- Aug 2011)/ Coporate Revenue Manager (Jan 2008 - Jun 2010)\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(us,84)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2008-1至2011-8\"},{\"locationName\":\"美国 旧金山湾区\",\"companyName\":\"92Cloud\",\"description\":\"*Provide financial and strategic guidance\",\"title\":\"Co Founder\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(us,84)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2015-7\"}]', '[\"Forecasting\",\"Financial Analysis\",\"Financial Reporting\",\"Revenue Recognition\"]', 'suwang', '2017-05-17 16:04:40');
