cription\":\"-Organize and lead sales and purchase team for the company\\n-Develop domestic sales channels and distributors\\n-Develop supply channels for elevator components\\n-Set-up whole cost sheet and quoting system\\n-Sales documentation including RFQ sheet, purchase contract, delivery notes etc.\\n-Support distributor and regional sales bidding activities \\n\",\"title\":\"Sales and Purchase Manager\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(cn,8909)\",\"rangeDate\":\"1998-3至2000-5\"}]', '[\"Manufacturing\",\"Sales Management\",\"New Business Development\",\"Business Strategy\"]', 'wang-fulton-88234820', '2017-05-17 16:05:03');
