INSERT INTO `linkedin_data` VALUES ('50765', 'PinGang', 'Zhang', '市场营销和广告', 'Sales Director 销售总监', '四川 成都', '[]', '[{\"locationName\":\"China Shanghai;Sichuan Chengdu;Yunnan Province;Guizhou Provice\",\"companyName\":\"Unilever personal care company 联合利华个人清洁护理用品公司\",\"description\":\"In Western Yunnan province were responsible for the management of the market (1998 - 1999), Sichuan Province area market (2000 - 2003). Had achieved a growth rate of 117% achievement rate in Sichuan Province ranked market annual sales target, in the team 9 sales colleagues in second; won the Lux brand salesperson of honor.\\nMain duties:\\n1 Overall management area within the sales staff, distributors, sales channels and terminal customers, according to the company\'s sales policies and development plans to lead sales team to achieve sales target and distribution.\\n2 set up and lead a sales team, sales staff training, guidance, motivation, assessment of their sales performance to help them grown, build efficient team spirit.\\n\\nUnilever Marketing Specialist (1996/01 - 1998/01)\\nTrade marketing management of Sichuan, Yunnan, Guizhou, Chongqing. Report line manager is the marketing director.\\nMain duties:\\n1 the operation of the market to provide services such as product manager, market, promotion, research, media reports to the market and the marketing department.\\n2 To be organization and management of regional market activities.\\n3 monitor and coordinate regional sales progress and media planning, market planning and plan execution management, advertising and promotional activities.\\n4 the training of sales staff product knowledge, collect the competitor\'s information.\\n\\n先后负责管理云南省滇西地区市场（1998—1999），四川省地区市场（2000—2003）。曾在四川省市场年度销售目标完成率的排名中获得增长率117%的成绩，位列团队9名销售同事中的第二名；曾获得力士品牌推广最佳销售人员的荣誉。 \\n主要职责： \\n1． 全面管理地区内的销售人员、分销商、销售渠道及终端客户，根据公司的销售政策和发展计划领导销售队伍完成公司销售和分销目标。\\n2． 选择和指定分销商，实现产品预定的分销覆盖及销售的增长和分销网络的建立。 \\n3． 建立和领导销售队伍，培训、指导销售人员，激励、评估其销售业绩以帮助其成长，塑造高效的团队精神。 \\n4． 建立和管理地区内的重点客户，通过熟练的陈述、分析和谈判技巧与其建立良好的合作伙伴关系。 \\n5． 根据公司计划组织和落实产品推广方案，确保促销活动高速有效的进行。 \\n联合利华市场专员（1996/01—1998/01） \\n管理四川、云南、贵州、重庆的市场推广工作。直线汇报给全国市场总监。 \\n主要职责： \\n1． 提供市场运作服务给产品经理，如提供市场、促销、调研、媒介报告给市场和通路行销部门。 \\n2． 组织和管理地区内的市场活动。 \\n3． 监控、协调地区销售的进展和媒介计划的实施，管理市场计划和方案，执行广告推广活动。 \\n4． 培训销售队伍产品知识，收集竞争对手的市场信息。\",\"title\":\"Sales Manager in Southwest region/Unilever Marketing Specialist\",\"rangeDate\":\"1996-1至2003-5\"},{\"locationName\":\"Guangzhou Guangdong Province\",\"companyName\":\"Triumph Hainan underwear Co. Ltd.\",\"description\":\"Responsible for the management of area: Guangdong, Guangxi, Hainan, Hunan, Fujian, Jiangxi, Sichuan, Yunnan, Guizhou, Chongqing 10 provinces and cities. Reported to the national sales manager and manage the 10 sales staff below. \\nAchievement:\\nComplete the AMO brand successfully entered the Metro, Wal-Mart, Carrefour, PARKnSHOP, Trust-Mart and RT-Mart and other key account. Achieved the AMO brand sales in modern trade increased from 1.03 million per month to 3.5 million per month.Complete national sales target year 6430 million.\\nMain duties:\\nOverall responsibility for sales management products, Set up AMO brand sales strategy \\nGuide and assist the branch to complete the sales target. Complete monthly Sales forecast\\nCooperate with marketing department to formulate the promotion plan and sales target.\\n\\n负责管理地区：广东、广西、海南、湖南、福建、江西、四川、云南、贵州、重庆10个省市。直线汇报给全国销售经理，下属销售人员10名。将美梦品牌成功进入麦德龙、沃尔玛、家乐福、百佳、好又多和大润发等多家重点客户；将美梦品牌在现代通路的销售业绩由103万/月增长至350万/月；完成年度全国销售目标6430万元。 \\n主要职责： \\n1． 全面负责美梦产品的销售管理工作，制定美梦产品的销售政策。 \\n2． 指导和协助各分公司完成美梦的销售目标。制定年度/每月的销售预测。 \\n3． 与市场部合作制定促销计划及产品的销售分配计划。 \\n4． 客户关系的维护及管理, 拓展产品的销售渠道。 \\n5． 与重点客户及主要经销商进行交易条款和合同的谈判。\",\"title\":\"Sales Manager (AMO brand)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2003-5至2005-5\"},{\"locationName\":\"Southwest，Northwest\",\"companyName\":\"Qingdao TaiShidai Collagen(skin care) Co. Ltd.\",\"description\":\"Managed the sales operation in Southwest and northwest such as Sichuan, Chongqing, Yunnan, Guizhou, Shanxi, Gansu, Xinjiang, Hunan .\\nBe responsible for the management and control in the region business coverage, channel development, sales, sales team management and motivation, dealer management, cost of sales, cost effective control and positive cash flow.\\nRole:\\nA) Be the driving force for business development region, shoulder to promote business development responsibilities.\\nB) Be a regional sales team leader, as the team direction, your training skills, they can trust.\\nC) Be a representative of the company, in the market, in front of the customer, in the middle of the team is reflected in the company\'s brand image and value.\\nDealer management:\\n-- According to the brand and sales development strategy, evaluation of regional distributor partners and responsible for the communication of information and the brand strategy, promote the implementation of the company\'s brand dealer sales strategy\\nSupervise dealers -- development of distribution network, and to improve the key customers and store service\\nDistribution management:\\n-- According to the district development level and economic income, choose the best distribution channel and distribution network\\nAccording to company\'s channel strategy and brand strategy, training and guidance to dealers and sales team corresponding channel operating skills and operating standards and inspection of the implementation\\n\\n管理西南四川、重庆、云南、贵州；西北陕西、甘肃、新疆；湖南区域。 \\n\\n负责所在大区的业务覆盖、渠道发展、销售业绩、销售团队管理与激励、经销商管理、销售费用的管理和控制,成本的有效控制和良性的现金周转。 \\n角色： \\na)是大区业务发展的动力,肩负着推动业务发展的责任. \\nb)是大区销售队伍的领袖,为你的队伍指引方向、训练技能,是他们可以信赖的人. \\nc)是公司的代表,在市场中、在客户面前、在队伍中间处处体现着公司品牌的形象和价值. \\n经销商管理: \\n--根据品牌销售发展策略，选择评估区域经销商合作伙伴并负责沟通公司信息及品牌策略，推动经销商执行公司的品牌销售策略 \\n--指导监督经销商发展分销网络，并提高对重点客户和商店的服务 \\n分销管理： \\n--根据大区发展水平及经济收入状况，选择最佳的分销渠道和分销网络 \\n--根据公司的渠道策略和品牌策略，培训和指导经销商及销售团队相对应渠道操作技巧和操作标准并予以检查实施 \\n销售队伍管理： \\n--根据品牌销售策略，建立大区销售队伍管理系统，加强渠道及业务管理 \\n--负责销售人员的招聘、培训、激励和发展 \\n\",\"title\":\"Regional Sales Manager-- West\",\"rangeDate\":\"2008-2至2012-12\"},{\"locationName\":\"Chengdu\",\"companyName\":\"Mengding Agricultural Industry Co., Ltd.\",\"description\":\"1, high-level management positions, to assist GM to develop the company\'s development strategy, which is responsible for the functional areas within the short and long term business decisions and strategies to achieve a significant impact on the company\'s long-term goals\\n2, responsible for the company\'s business development, sales operations, can be a powerful program into results\\n3, set sales targets, sales model, marketing strategy, sales budget and incentive programs\\n4, the establishment and management of the sales force, standardized sales process, sales target\\n5, analysis of new and existing distribution system or market potential sales channels, sales and expenses, profit and loss calculations\\n6, focus on maintaining and enhancing the market competitiveness\\n7, responsible for planning the company\'s annual market objectives and marketing program\\n8, responsible for developing the business market, the associated promotion, including the management and promotion of the progress of the establishment of the company\'s operation of the market system\\n9, analysis and forecasting sales market, grasp market trends, to provide accurate information for decision-making, to explore and develop the sales market\\n10, budget planning and management of market activity, rational and effective, maximize the use of the budget\\nSubordinate departments: sales (distribution, direct sales, E-commerce, Group buy, special channel) and the Market\\nAchievement\\nCo-operate with 1919 alcohol direct supply O2O platform (which is a domestic liquor distribution industry public companies)\\nCo-operate with WSmall.com which is a e-business internet company with over 60,000 WeChat Dealers community\\nAchieved selling 16,000 products in 48 hours in WSmall.com\\n1、高层管理职位，协助决策层制定公司发展战略，负责短期及长期的公司决策和战略，对公司中长期目标的达成产生重要影响\\n2、负责公司的业务拓展、销售运作，设置销售目标、销售模式、销售战略、销售预算和奖励计划\\n3、建立和管理销售队伍，规范销售流程，完成销售目标\\n5、负责策划公司年度市场工作目标和营销方案\\n6、负责开拓市场业务，进行相关的宣传推广，包括管理以及进度的推进，建立公司的市场运作体制\\n7、规划和管理市场活动的预算，合理有效、最大限度地使用预算\\n下属部门：销售部（流通、直销、电商、团购、特渠）和市场部\",\"title\":\"Sales Director 销售总监\",\"rangeDate\":\"2015-10\"},{\"locationName\":\"Beijing\",\"companyName\":\"DKT international Co., Ltd. (Beijing)\",\"description\":\"In DKT International, founded in 1980, in Washington, is a company dedicated to human health, providing International institutions on reproductive health products and services.\\nAchievement：\\nComplete marketing plan and sales strategy with Mojo brand, Prudence brand.\\nQuickly realize the distribution products in North, Northeast, Southwest region and achieve more than 1,000 outlets to display and sale.\\n\\n1. Assist the general manager to establish the company\'s development strategy; according to company strategic development planning, organization, implementation of the strategy of business development plan and sales company, management and sales target\\n2. Responsible for the company\'s business development, sales operations, can be planned into a strong result\\n3. Set sales targets, sales mode, sales strategy, sales budget and reward plan\\n4. Analysis and explore potential market, establish and maintain good relationship with customers\\n5. Build team, staff recruitment and conducted internal / external training. Improved professionalism of staff, supervise and evaluate team performance.\\n\\nDKT International于1980年在美国首都华盛顿成立，是一家致力于人类健康，提供有关生殖健康产品及服务的国际机构。 \\n　　DKT International倡导避孕防性病的观念，在许多国家发展和实施了多项计划生育、生殖健康及预防性病、艾滋病的项目。 \\n　　DKT International及其姐妹机构PSI（Population Service International）、MSI (Marie Stope International)遍布全球，在近40个国家中设有分支机构，DKT的努力及成就，及对当地国所作出的贡献，得到了所在国政府及许多国际机构的支持和赞赏。其中有世界银行、联合国人口基金、USAID、DFID、FHI、KFW、Sida/Forum Syd、AIDSMark、荷兰基金、 Packard基金和盖茨基金等。 \\n　　DKT在很多国家开展工作：墨西哥，巴西，摩洛哥，埃及，苏丹，加纳，埃塞俄比亚，莫桑比克，刚果民主共和国，土耳其，印度，巴基斯坦，尼日利亚，印度尼西亚，马来西亚，越南，泰国，中国，菲律宾。秉持着低收入人群也能体面获得高质量、可负担避孕产品和服务的理念，DKT发展至今，已成长为立足发展中国家、最大的生殖健康服务和产品的独立供应商。\\nDKT北京致力于在中国开展计划生育服务以及艾滋病防治，推广优质并且价格合理的安全套以及其他生殖健康产品。DKT北京2012年进入中国市场。\\n\\n1.协助总经理制定公司的发展战略；根据公司战略发展规划制定、组织、实施公司经营发展计划和销售战略，实现经营管理和销售业务的目标 \\n2.负责公司业务拓展，销售运作，能强有力的将计划转变成结果 \\n3.设置销售目标、销售模式、销售战略、销售预算和奖励计划 \\n4.建立和管理销售队伍，规范销售流程，完成销售目标 \\n5.分析和发掘市场潜力，建立并保持与客户群的良好合作关系 \\n6.营销团队建设，人员招聘，内/外部培训，员工专业化素质提升，内部绩效考核的监督考评 \\n7.主持公司重大营销合同的谈判和签订工作 \\n8.协调各部门资源，妥善处理市场出现的各类事件\",\"title\":\"Salrs Director\",\"rangeDate\":\"2013-12至2015-3\"}]', '[\"sales and market management\",\"管理人员\",\"领导力\",\"顾客服务\"]', 'pingang-zhang-056222118', '2017-05-17 16:06:04');
