in for the better life quality of GBM patients.\\n\\nHighlights of my current work:\\n•\\tInvestigated influence of anti-angiogenic therapy on drug delivery to brain tumors using patient derived xenograft model in collaboration with Dr. Jann N. Sarkaria in Mayo Clinic\\n•\\tResearched pre-clinical brain/plasma concentration PK/PD of molecularly targeted anti-cancer therapy \\n•\\tManaged laboratory functions including organization, ordering and daily maintenance etc.\\n•\\tEstablished and validated assay protocols and tutored graduate students\\n\",\"title\":\"Postdoctoral Associate\",\"rangeDate\":\"2014-1至2015-9\"}]', '[\"Western Blotting\",\"In Vivo\",\"Cell Culture\",\"In Vitro\"]', 'shuanglingzhang', '2017-05-17 16:06:33');
