subcompany in India and together worked on for Saudi Arabia SWCC CCPP project 2400MW.\\nJuly - December at 2012, was sent to Dubai worked together with Simens engineers and USA Sargent Lundy（S&L）engineer for the Aramco IPP project.\\nAt 2013, Was sent to construction site at the Saudi Arabia for the SWCC CCPP 2400MW project for I&C construction and design technical supporting.\\nAt 2014, Mainly responsible for the CFB 3X35MW project in Indonesia.\\nAt the same time at 2015, I am also responsible for checking the detailed drawing of the NOOR II CSP POWER PLANT in Morocco. This project We worked together with Sener design institute company of Spain. \\n\",\"title\":\"I&C chief engineer\",\"rangeDate\":\"2008-3\"}]', '[\"familiar power plant process flow\",\"project manage\",\"I&C and electrical design\",\"EPC design consultation\"]', 'zhang-guozheng-63bb5a9a', '2017-05-17 16:06:47');
