mand team - managing high yield for our Publishers.\\n\\nI manage the Asia Pacific office. We focus on Demand Side Platforms, Ad Networks and Mobile Media owners (Premium, popular as well as local Mobile Apps/Sites).\\n\\nI primarily help Mobile App developers and Publishers maximize revenue through paid advertising.\",\"title\":\"Business Development Manager, Supply APAC\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(sg,0)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2014-5至2015-12\"},{\"locationName\":\"新加坡\",\"companyName\":\"Havas Media\",\"title\":\"Assistant Digital Manager\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(sg,0)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2013-8至2013-12\"},{\"locationName\":\"新加坡\",\"companyName\":\"Smaato\",\"description\":\"Smaato is a Global Mobile monetization platform running one of the largest Mobile Real Time Bidding (RTB) exchanges and Supply Side Platform (SSP) mediation platforms.\\n\\nI play an active role in on boarding and educating new media partnerships to engage them in monetization via mobile advertising and marketing. I am the go-to-person for consultations in mobile marketing activities with new Clients as well as an existing portfolio of established Clients. \\n\\nApart from that, I travel regularly to manage Partnership relationships and spreading the word of Smaato within APAC, with my focus on expanding the Chinese-speaking markets. This is a great opportunity for me, who loves a fun and fast paced environment with lots to learn about mobile marketing.\\n\",\"title\":\"Senior Manager, Supply Business Development - APAC\",\"region\":\"urn:li:fs_region:(sg,0)\",\"rangeDate\":\"2016-1至2016-8\"}]', '[\"Online Advertising\",\"SEM\",\"PPC\",\"Google Analytics\"]', 'gladyszhang', '2017-05-17 16:13:33');
